Reasoning: 
1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the achievable rate performance of a VFD relaying system, which is a key topic in information theory. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the design and optimization of a relay system, which is a fundamental aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a joint tuning of design parameters to improve the system performance, which is a key aspect of systems and control. 
4. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking) - The paper deals with the design and optimization of a communication system, which is a key topic in communication and networking. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the behavior of the proposed system through extensive simulation results, which is a key aspect of multimedia research.
